1. *Lice* je mnogo prilično. (The face is very pretty.)
2. Otac mu je uzimao *lica*. (His father was taking faces.)
3. Ona je zamišljala lepa *lica*. (She was imagining beautiful faces.)
4. Ja sam videla dve bele *lica*. (I saw two white faces.)
5. Ona je otkrila svoje skriveno *lice*. (She revealed her hidden face.)
6. Prostor je pun *lica*. (The room was full of faces.)
7. Ona je gledala u *lice* neznanca. (She was looking at the face of a stranger.)
8. On je mogao da primeti *lice* svoje majke. (He could recognize his mother's face.)